high_descs: Turn left and walk to the table then turn left and walk to the garbage.
Pick up the pen under the light at the edge of the table.
Take a half step to your left.
Put the pen in the garbage.
Turn around and walk to the bed then turn left and walk to the wall turn left walk to the wall then turn left and take a step towards the table.
Pick up the pen that's near the right of the laptop.
Walk back over to where you put the first pen.
Put this pen in the garbage too.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens in the garbage.

high_descs: Turn around and face the trash can in front of the desk.
Pick the pencil up from the desk to the right.
Move to the left and face the trash can.
Put the pencil in the trash can.
Turn around and stand behind the desk.
Pick the pencil up from the desk.
Move around the desk to face the trash can.
Put the pencil in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils in a trash can.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the left side of the desk.
Pick up the pen on the desk that is close to the edge and in front of the lamp in the corner.
Walk closer to the garbage can on the floor in front of you.
Place the pen in the garbage can in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the end of the desk, then make a left and go to the corner of the desk, and turn left again so that you are on the other side of the desk.
Pick up the pen on the desk,  between the lap top and the wall.
Turn to your left and walk to the end of the desk, turn right again and go to the corner of the desk, then make another right and go to the garbage can on the floor.
Put the pen in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put two pens, from opposite sides of the desk, into the garbage can.
